# Firebase / Online Sync

## Data paths

```
rooms/{roomId}/timestamp | image | lines/{id}/points,isDrawing,timestamp | view/
```

## Patterns

- DB refs via `useDatabaseRef` (created once per mount)
- Drawing: local `setLines` + remote `set`/`update` on `points` indices
- Image: Storage `uploadBytes` → `getDownloadURL` → RTDB `image`

## Hotspot

`OnlineCanvas.tsx` (~330 lines) centralizes sync and view sharing. Change with care.

## Known issues (verify before fixing)

- Line 161: `Object.keys(lines)` is wrong for Immutable `Lines`; stale closure in `useEffect([])`
- View mode typo `"follwer"` is intentional until migration plan exists

## Security

No auth. Do not widen `database.rules.json` or `storage.rules`.

## Local development

Use `npm run dev:emulator` or set `VITE_USE_FIREBASE_EMULATOR=true` with `npm run emulators`.
